{"tid":1999565,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"喜茶港8間分店只剩2間　職員：應該唔會再開","createTime":"2020-05-03T09:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T09:26:15.000Z","uid":307021,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d493953ed310b9917e2b5d4041f23d178e46c8","tid":1999565,"uid":307021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"2018年進軍香港時紅極一時的內地茶飲店「喜茶」（HEYTEA），自去年6月起爆發反修例事件，網民抵制內地品牌後，本港生意可謂一落千丈。喜茶在港有8間分店，惟近期6間分店連環停業，位於尖沙咀的3間分店更疑似全線「執笠」。本報記者今日（3日）以顧客身分致電目前正在營業、位於沙田新城市廣場的喜茶分店，職員確認喜茶目前在港仍有營運的分店只有兩間，更指其他分店「應該唔會再開」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200503/4UXWOW73T7IEEUURNPJ5PMEXP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200503%2F4UXWOW73T7IEEUURNPJ5PMEXP4%2F&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjghn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=f782cf46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200503%2F4UXWOW73T7IEEUURNPJ5PMEXP4%2F&h=abee615a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200503/4UXWOW73T7IEEUURNPJ5PMEXP4/</a>"},{"pid":"f6ba2b2e502a4bc3ccae3df4bfe2e3d9c01e056d","tid":1999565,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c4f5004b618d95d797882b70edfe0e1a131b47","tid":1999565,"uid":286817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"快啲執柒埋嗰兩間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}